org.openflow.protocol

Class OFMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openflow.protocol.OFMessage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OFBarrierReply, OFBarrierRequest, OFCounterMod, OFCounterReply, OFCounterRequest, OFEchoRequest, OFError, OFExperimenter, OFFeaturesReply, OFFeaturesRequest, OFFlowMod, OFFlowRemoved, OFFlowTableResource, OFGetAsyncReply, OFGetAsyncRequest, OFGetConfigRequest, OFGroupMod, OFHello, OFMeterMod, OFPacketIn, OFPacketOut, OFPortStatus, OFQueueGetConfigReply, OFQueueGetConfigRequest, OFRoleReply, OFRoleRequest, OFSetAsync, OFStatisticsMessageBase, OFSwitchConfig, OFTableMod

    public class OFMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    The base class for all OpenFlow protocol messages. This class contains the equivalent of the ofp_header which is present in all OpenFlow messages.
    Author:
    David Erickson (daviderickson@cs.stanford.edu) - Feb 3, 2010, Rob Sherwood (rob.sherwood@stanford.edu) - Feb 3, 2010
